Instructions:

To remove Starforce******** Go into the game directory and find the Protect icon with the key. Right click and select &quot;Remove SF driver&quot; uninstall and reboot PC.

Add crack files to game after reboot!


To make the game fully in English:

#1. Rename the following folders [Blackshark] [FUI] [l10n] [Missions] [Sounds] (I always use &quot;_&quot; in front of them so I have them just where they are supposed to be: [_Blackshark] [_FUI] [_l10n] [_Missions] [_Sounds])

#2. Copy (Do not move them, always keep the originals in case something goes wrong and you have to revert and try again) those folders from the English &quot;patch&quot; to the Russian version.

#3. To get the training menu in English:
a. Go to BlackSharkDataScriptsTraining
b. You should have 2 files there:
TrainingData.lua and TrainingData_ru.lua
c. Rename the TrainingData_ru.lua to something else (like &quot;_TrainingData_ru.lua&quot;) or make another folder inside that one and move it there) so only the English file is in the folder.
d. That's it, training missions menu should be in English.

#4. For the Encyclopedia:
a. Go to BlackSharkDataScriptsEnc
b. You should have a folder for each different category of objects (helicopters, planes, etc.).
c. Inside each one of those folders you should see 2 sets of files, one in English &quot;FileName.txt&quot; and &quot;FileName_ru.txt&quot;.
d. Rename (or move to another folder) all files ending in &quot;_ru.txt&quot;. I prefer to create a sub-folder inside each folder, call it &quot;bck&quot; and move the file there?s so in case I need them, I know they are one folder bellow where they should be, but that's up to you.
e. That's it. Encyclopedia should be in English.

#5. To get the rest of the screens in English, go to the &quot;binstable&quot; folder, rename the files Common.dll, Cosmos.dll and lua*.dll and copy those files from the English installation.

#6. If you want to get rid of Russian missions, go to the Mission folders and do the same to each name with &quot;strange&quot; characters (I believe they should be in Russian but since we don't have the fonts we see them this way).

#7. If you want the cockpit in English you will need to dl the mod installer tool and do it that way.
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.backup.lockonfiles.com/modules/Downloads/fileuploads/ModMan7110.zip#dl&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.backup.lockonfiles.com/modules/Downloads/fileuploads/ModMan7110.zip#dl&lt;/a&gt;

To make the menu in English,navigate to [Install_Path]l10n, and rename folder RU to RU1 to make main screen in English.


Notes: If you have an ATI card, go into CCC and disable Catalyst AI. I had problems runing the game with my 3870x2 untill I disabled it.
